Here are some example questions and answers:

I gave my students this multiple choice question:
Baadhi ya maeneo ya dunia yanakabiliwa na hali kama za jangwa. Mabadiliko haya yanapendelea zaidi maisha ya spishi zenye uwezo wa kufanya nini kati ya yafuatayo?
Only one answer is correct among these 4 choices:

Options:
A: kutumia kiasi kikubwa cha chakula
B: kuwa katika hali ya kutulia kwa vipindi virefu
C: kutambua miale isiyoonekana na mionzi-urujuani
D: kupitisha maji kupitia ngozi hadi kwenye angahewa

Could you tell me which one is correct?B

I gave my students this multiple choice question:
Darasa moja linachunguza jinsi mazoezi ya mwili yanavyoathiri mpigo wa moyo. Mapigo ya moyo ya wanafunzi wawili kabla ya kufanya mazoezi yalinganishwa na mapigo yao ya moyo baada ya kukimbia kwenye uwanja wa michezo. Ni utaratibu gani utakaosaidia darasa kulinganisha kwa usahihi matokeo ya wanafunzi hao wawili?
Only one answer is correct among these 4 choices:

Options:
A: kupima wanafunzi wenye urefu sawa
B: kufanya wanafunzi kukimbia siku moja sawa
C: pima umbali ambao kila mwanafunzi anakimbia
D: kufanya wanafunzi wakimbie kwa muda sawa

Could you tell me which one is correct?D

I gave my students this multiple choice question:
Felicia alichunguza ikiwa rangi ya maji iliathiri jinsi maji yalivyopashwa joto haraka katika mwanga wa jua. Alimimina maji ya bomba kwenye viriba vitano na kuweka rangi ya chakula katika viriba vinne kati ya vitano. Kisha Felicia alitumia kipimajoto kupima halijoto ya maji katika kila kiriba. Ni ipi kati ya hizi ilitumika kama udhibiti katika uchunguzi wake?
Only one answer is correct among these 4 choices:

Options:
A: kuchanganya rangi ya chakula katika maji
B: kupima kiriba cha maji ya bomba yasiyo na rangi
C: kutumia kiasi sawa cha maji katika kila jaribio
D: kupima sampuli za maji ya rangi katika nyakati tofauti

Could you tell me which one is correct?B

I gave my students this multiple choice question:
Howie aliweka mimea yake chini ya mwanga wa mmea. Alikuwa akisaidia mimea yake kufanya nini kwa kuiweka kwenye mwanga?
Only one answer is correct among these 4 choices:

Options:
A: kutengeneza chakula
B: kuvutia wadudu
C: kutoa chavua
D: kukuza mizizi

Could you tell me which one is correct?A

I gave my students this multiple choice question:
Ikiwa kilo 1 ya msombo wa toluini inayeyuka kwa -95°C, basi 500 g ya toluini
Only one answer is correct among these 4 choices:

Options:
A: itayeyuka kwa -47.5°C.
B: itayeyuka kwa -95°C.
C: itachemka kwa 95°C.
D: itachmka kwa 47.5°C.

Could you tell me which one is correct?B
